name.message: c note Add Web Page Content to MD Note

description.message: Right_click on the selected content and choose 'Add Content to New Note' to add the content to the side note.

description1.message: Welcome to the c note extension!

description2.message: This extension allows you to select content while browsing and add it to your notes.

description3.message: Right_click on the selected content and choose 'Add Content to New Note' to add the content to the note.

description4.message: Also supports exporting to .md, .pdf, .html, .docx, .txt formats or saving online (supports cloud synchronization).
